headline: Expedia Group to Webcast Fourth Quarter 2024 Results on February 6, 2025
summary: SEATTLE, January 13, 2025--Expedia Group (NASDAQ: EXPE) will report its fourth quarter 2024 results for the period ended December 31, 2024, on Thursday, February 6, 2025 via an earnings release and accompanying webcast. These items will be available in the Investor Relations section of the company’s corporate website at http://ir.expediagroup.com.
